snippet.title: Launch Gameplay Trailer | Official Call of Duty: Black Ops 4
snippet.description:
On October 12, the world goes black. It’s time to soldier up. For Black Ops at its best. 

✅ All-new Blackout Battle Royale mode
✅ The next evolution of Multiplayer 
✅ 3 Zombies Experiences

Pre-order Call of Duty®: Black Ops 4 now, available October 12th on PS4, Xbox One, and PC: bit.ly/PreOrderBO4

Song: Welcome To The Party - Diplo, French Montana & Lil Pump ft. Zhavia  Listen here: http://smarturl.it/wttp

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
Twitter: http://twitter.com/CallofDuty
Instagram: http://instagram.com/callofduty
Facebook: http://facebook.com/CallofDuty
